My name is Patrick Foster. I teach at [[Central Connecticut State University]], and I often edit articles associated with CCSU. I do not, however, and will not, use this site to promote a one-sided view of the university. My hope is to provide accurate historical information which others can use, edit, and improve upon. I think that in the long run, CCSU will be best represented not by vigilant removal of unfavorable information (and I don't think we do that), but via openness and transparency. This is the politically-correct view among wikipedians, but not among the PR staffs at what seems to be an increasing number of US colleges and universities.

